title: Plastics and Rubber Machinery (Euromap)
description: OPC 40077 (Euromap 77): Data exchange between injection moulding machines (IMM) and MES Manufacturing execution systems (MES) are used for collecting the information generated by IMM at a central point for easier quality assurance and job and dataset management.
